{
  "3268520": {
    "name": "Before Exit: Gas Station",
    "steam_appid": 3268520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/03d68dc5b62f58dae76c10b9923632a4.poster.avif?t=1771581162\" width=1170 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/03d68dc5b62f58dae76c10b9923632a4.webm?t=1771581162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/03d68dc5b62f58dae76c10b9923632a4.mp4?t=1771581162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>《离场前：加油站》</strong>是一款氛围浓郁且充满意外转折的异常检测游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">要揭开所有秘密并彻底理解它，你需要多次通关整个战役。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/55369e5d848f5fe84d08dfbf6962dcf5.poster.avif?t=1771581162\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/55369e5d848f5fe84d08dfbf6962dcf5.webm?t=1771581162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/55369e5d848f5fe84d08dfbf6962dcf5.mp4?t=1771581162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>《离场前：加油站》</strong>中，你将扮演加油站员工，每晚执行关店任务。等等，加油站不是通宵营业的吗？在这个世界可不！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >老板极度严苛且热衷节省开支。夜幕降临即意味着熄灯关店、打烊回家。这座偏僻加油站深处荒野，天黑后岂会有人光顾？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/90fcefc2335573005e4ce4bae876a1af.poster.avif?t=1771581162\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/90fcefc2335573005e4ce4bae876a1af.webm?t=1771581162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/90fcefc2335573005e4ce4bae876a1af.mp4?t=1771581162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 40余个剧情丰富的场景，满载独特内容，4种不同结局，外加6个神秘额外章节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔁 反复游玩解锁全部内容，揭开真实结局。你准备好回家了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 首发支持14种语言，完整Steam成就系统及手柄操作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >延续前作特色，本作将Roguelike元素与逻辑谜题融合于独特的异常检测题材！日复一日寻找所有任务，在归家前完成所有目标...回家？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/2a7353e3c324f82342d1d94b871054eb.poster.avif?t=1771581162\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/2a7353e3c324f82342d1d94b871054eb.webm?t=1771581162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/2a7353e3c324f82342d1d94b871054eb.mp4?t=1771581162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作更首度允许你在返家前真正离开工作场所！检查加油机，清理油渍，赶走那些妄想最后一刻加油的顾客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成所有任务让老板满意。切勿出错——他观察力极强，你离被解雇仅有一步之遥。总之，在这迷人的工作场所享受美好时光吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras/997de363dc9229ff9985fce8fb681edc.avif?t=1771581162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268520/extras_big/997de363dc9229ff9985fce8fb681edc.webp?t=1771581162 width=1560 height=494 /></span></p>",
